title: JOJOGOGO Mardi Gras Decorations Outdoor Throw Pillow Covers 18x18 Waterproof Set of 4 Happy Mardi Gras Fat Tuesday Decor Carnival Theme Masquerade Party Decorations for Front Porch and Patio Furniture
features: ⚜【Mardi Gras Outdoor Decorations】 If you change pillow covers, flags and rugs on your front porch every holiday season and want these outdoor decorations to last a little longer, waterproof fabric might be a better choice for you. These cute mardi gras holiday waterproof pillow covers are perfect for decorating patio furniture, porch swing, balcony, garden or yard. Easy to match with other mardi gras party decorations outdoor.

⚜【Happy Mardi Gras】 Set of 4 Outdoor Mardi Gras Throw Pillow Covers ( The Pillow Inserts Are Not Included ) with parade vehicles, mask and fleur de lis elements. Each measures about 18 x 18 inches. Since it is hand cut and sewn, please allow 0.5 inch size deviation.

⚜【Waterproof Decorative Throw Pillows】 vibrant color waterproof throw pillow cover made of water/oil/stain resistant fabric. A premium polyester linen blend beige material (Burlap-like fabric), very sturdy and ideal for outdoor use. Soft and thick enough to cover any colored insert, they looked nice enough for the month of carnival season! Beige Color Material not white.

⚜【Pattern Printed on One Side Only】 The colors are bright and the material is durable, only one side is printed with a vivid pattern, and the other side is pure beige. There is an invisible zipper at the bottom, which makes it easy to remove or insert the pillow filler.
⚜【Wash & Care】 Hand wash or machine wash in cold water separately. Gently cycle only and don't bleach, tumble dry. Do not iron. After washing, it will not fade, pucker or wrinkle.
description: This set of porch decorative pillow covers can be used as porch decor for the whole month of carnival season. Pillows look so pretty in your outdoor rooms, on your patios, porches and stoops.Made of durable polyester with PU coating, waterproof and durable.This water-resistant fabric is available for outdoor use in the garden.But in order to prolong the service life of the pillow case, please do not let it rain for a long time.Invisible zipper allows the inserts can be inserted and removed from the covers easily.No Pillow Inserts! Set of 4 Outdoor Waterproof Pillow Covers 18x18 inch Only.These outdoor pillow covers can not only protect your pillows from water and sun but also lighten up your front porch.Good decorations for garden, patio, balcony, living room etc and suitable for all kinds of indoor or outdoor furniture.Hand wash or machine wash separately in cold water on the gentle cycle, tumble dry low, do not bleach.
